| Detection 1: PowerShell Execution Policy Bypass (T1059.001)
| Trigger: powershell.exe launched with -ExecutionPolicy Bypass
| Severity: High
| ATT&CK: T1059.001 - Command and Scripting Interpreter: PowerShell

index=main source="WinEventLog:Microsoft-Windows-Sysmon/Operational"
| rex field=_raw "CommandLine'>(?<CommandLine>[^<]+)"
| rex field=_raw "Image'>(?<Image>[^<]+)"
| search Image="*powershell*" CommandLine="*ExecutionPolicy Bypass*"
| table _time, Image, CommandLine
| sort _time
